OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will remain
OL,8,Fdry with some lengthy clear periods.
OL,9,FLight winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,12,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,13,Fbubbling up by afternoon. Warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FAll
OL,16,Fparts will see a dry and quite sunny
OL,17,Ffew days. Becoming very warm. Light
OL,18,Fwinds.
